	    <!-- Dialog -->
	    <string name="help_input">If you have some raw text that you want to analyze, click <b><i>Enter Text</i></b> and type or paste your text into the box on the screen. If your text is saved in a plain text file on your device, click <b><i>Import File</i></b> and locate your file using the navigation section that appears above. Select your native language by clicking <b><i>Select Language</i></b> and choosing from the list. Then click <b><i>Submit</i></b>, and your results will appear on the next page once processing is complete. Clicking <b><i>Recent</i></b> will show you the results of your most recent analyzed input.</string>
    
